Class Sale

java.lang.Object
Sale
public class Sale extends Object
Author:
Katlyn Yoder The Sale class contains information and methods needed to keep track of all items added to the sale. There are several getter and setter methods to aid in storing and extracting of information for the sale. This class aids in developing the item list and totals for each item.
